      "content": "I am looking at the vibration and pressure logs for Turbine 4 right now too. They look normal, but the thermal reading is definitely climbing. If I call for a manual inspection and it turns out to be a sensor glitch, the whole line stays down for an hour for nothing. Are you sure you don't think it's just a calibration error? Can we just keep running for now?",
